      • FastMultiBinPacking

        public FastMultiBinPacking(choco.kernel.memory.IEnvironment environment,
                   choco.kernel.solver.variables.integer.IntDomainVar[][] loads,
                   int[][] sizes,
                   choco.kernel.solver.variables.integer.IntDomainVar[] bins)
        constructor of the FastBinPacking global constraint
        Parameters:
        environment - the solver environment
        loads - array of nbDims x nbBins variables, each figuring the total size of the items assigned to it, usually initialized to [0, capacity]
        sizes - array of nbDim x nbItems CONSTANTS ordered in decreasing order on the first dimension, each figuring the size of i-th item
        bins - array of nbItems variables, each figuring the possible bins an item can be assigned to, usually initialized to [0, nbBins-1]
